      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E92 BMW M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This example showcases flawless mechanical synchronization, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous response up to the 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are preserved through Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring peak lateral acceleration and traction. Meticulously serviced with preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator replacements, this carbon-roofed specimen retains its factory-delivered structural rigidity and aesthetic perfection. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking an unmolested, driver-centric masterpiece.",
